13781,IssuesEvent,2017-04-10 03:02:58+00:00,24375248,blockstack/blockstack-core,669932,muneeb-ali,8165984,blockstack,closed,Make the old resolver compatible with the new API ,[{'id': 269175553, 'url': 'https://api.github.com/repos/blockstack/blockstack-core/labels/api', 'name': 'api', 'color': '207de5', 'default': False}]","[{'login': 'muneeb-ali', 'id': 669932, 'avatar_url': 'https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/669932?v=3', 'gravatar_id': '', 'url': 'https://api.github.com/users/muneeb-ali', 'html_url': 'https://github.com/muneeb-ali', 'followers_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/muneeb-ali/followers', 'following_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/muneeb-ali/following{/other_user}', 'gists_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/muneeb-ali/gists{/gist_id}', 'starred_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/muneeb-ali/starred{/owner}{/repo}', 'subscriptions_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/muneeb-ali/subscriptions', 'organizations_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/muneeb-ali/orgs', 'repos_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/muneeb-ali/repos', 'events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/muneeb-ali/events{/privacy}', 'received_events_url': 'https://api.github.com/users/muneeb-ali/received_events', 'type': 'User', 'site_admin': False}]",0,We have an old resolver interface that ran as a separate system. Now we're merging it with the new API. It'd be great if the changes to that interface are minimal and other parties like OpenBazaar and the Onename API don't need to push changes at their end when we upgrade our resolver.,{},{}

